Package com.day.cq.workflow.model

Interface WorkflowTransition

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HasMetaData
    public interface WorkflowTransition
extends HasMetaData
    WorkflowTransition represents a transition between two WorkflowNodes of a WorkflowModel.
